<h1>Simple Scrambled Egg</h1>
<p> Simple Scrambled Egg is a quick and fluffy egg dish made by lightly beating eggs and cooking them in a pan with a little oil or butter. It's easy, tasty, and perfect for  a fast breakfast.</p>
<h2>Ingredients</h2>
<ul>
  <li>2 eggs</li>
<li>Salt</li>
<li>1 tablespoon milk (optional)</li>
<li>1 tablespoon oil/butter</li>
</ul>
<h2> Instructions</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Beat egg with a pinch of salt.<li>Heat pan and add oil.</li>
    <li>Pour the eggs and stir continuosly.</li>
    <li>Cook until soft and fluffy.</li>
    </ol>
